ORM: Map java class to database table.

JPA providers:
---------------
Hibernate implements JPA api by following the spec.
Spring data JPA is another provider.

- Two thing: Create EmployeeRepository that extends crud reposiroty and Create a domain obj and map it to table.

Ex:
---
1) 
Product
ProductRepository
Configure Data source connection info
-------
@Entity
@Table
public class Product{

    @Id
    private int id;
    private String name;
    @Column(name="description")
    private String desc;

}

2)
public interface ProductRepository extends CrudRepository<Product,Integer>{

}


3) DB configs: in application.properties

spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/mydb
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=test
spring.jpa.show-sql=true


